# Data Governor

This is the data governor, it's responsible for data pipeline management.


## Building locally

To build locally you will need openldap-devel, python2.7-devel, openssl-devel.

###OSX

* Install homebrew
ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)"

brew install python --framework
brew install pip
pip install virtualenv
pip install virtualenvwrapper
ln -s /u

make install

# To run unit tests 
make test

# To run data governor locally on your box
# talk to someone on the DPaaS team :-)
